expression.expression:
CASE WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'N/A' THEN 0
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Beginner' THEN 1
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Basic' THEN '2'
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Intermediate' THEN 3
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Proficient' THEN 4
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Advanced' THEN 5
     WHEN "PROFICIENCY_LABEL" ILIKE 'Expert' THEN 6
     ELSE NULL END

configOptions.importQuery:
SELECT MAX(fla."LAB_PERCENTAGE_CORRECT") as MAX_LAB_SCORE
	, MIN(fla."LAB_PERCENTAGE_CORRECT") as MIN_LAB_SCORE
	, fla."LAB_ID" as LAB_ID
	, fla."USER_ID" as USER_ID
	, fla."COURSE_ID" as COURSE_ID
	, fla."TENANT_ID" as TENANT_ID
FROM "DM_ENROLLMENT_SNAPSHOT_RC"."FACT_LAB_ACTIVITY" fla
JOIN "DM_ENROLLMENT_SNAPSHOT_RC"."DIM_LAB" dl
	ON fla."LAB_ID" = dl."LAB_ID"
GROUP BY fla."LAB_ID"
	, fla."USER_ID"
	, fla."COURSE_ID"
	, fla."TENANT_ID"

expression.expression:
CASE WHEN "RESULT" = 1 THEN 'Pass'
     WHEN "RESULT" = 0 THEN 'Fail' ELSE 'No Result Set' END

CASE WHEN "HAS_ACTIVE_LICENSES" = 1 THEN 'Current Groups'
ELSE 'All Groups' END

CASE WHEN "COURSE_TYPE" ILIKE 'Default' THEN 'BenchPrep Course'
     WHEN "COURSE_TYPE" ILIKE 'User-Portal Only' THEN 'Asset-Based Course' ELSE 'No Course Type Set' END

configOptions.importQuery:
SELECT MAX(fsr."SCORE") as MAX_SIMULATION_SCORE
, MIN(fsr."SCORE") as MIN_SIMULATION_SCORE
, fsr."SIMULATION_ID" as SIMULATION_ID
, fsr."USER_ID" as USER_ID
, fsr."COURSE_ID" as COURSE_ID
, fsr."TENANT_ID" as TENANT_ID
FROM "DM_ENROLLMENT_SNAPSHOT_RC"."FACT_SIMULATION_RESULT" fsr
GROUP BY fsr."SIMULATION_ID"
, fsr."USER_ID"
, fsr."COURSE_ID"
, fsr."TENANT_ID"
